Package: EMLassemblyline
Title: A workflow for creating EML
Version: 2.4.6
Authors@R: person("Colin", "Smith", email = "colin.smith@wisc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2261-9931")
Description: A set of functions facilitating a workflow to create metadata
    for a user supplied data entity. Templates are copied to the working
    directory and instructions prompt the user to provide requisite 
    information. The user selects from a collection of functions to extract
    information from the data entities, and finally executes a fancy wrapper
    function to build, validate, and write the EML metadata to file.
